<br>
Solinar, just a question for you if you dont mind.<br>
Since avg hit of emperor is 600(my own logs showed 593, so we got similar results on that) and with defensive, DI is reduced to DI/2, when DI = 32.7, you can easily calculate the avg hit with defensive is about 422.<br>
